Items.Title: A Local Law to amend the New York city charter, in relation to requiring that all documents that an agency is required by charter or other law to prepare, and the databases used to create such documents, be transmitted to the council as a computer file as well as in print copy.
Items.ActionText: This Introduction was Hearing Held by Committee
Items.MatterName: All documents that an agency is required by charter or other law to prepare, and the databases used to create such documents, be transmitted to the council as a computer file as well as in print copy.
